SchemeName.Name: SI:Supervision/Accreditation Status List of certification services from Certification Service Providers, which are supervised/accredited by the referenced Scheme Operator’s Member State for compliance with the relevant provisions laid down in Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures.

SI:Seznam statusov nadzora/akreditacije storitev overjanja s strani overiteljev, ki jih nadzoruje/akreditira upravljavec sheme zadevne države članice zaradi skladnosti z zadevnimi določbami Direktive Evropskega parlamenta in Sveta 1999/93/ES z dne 13. decembra 1999 o okviru Sklupnosti za elektronski podpis.

PolicyOrLegalNotice.TSLLegalNotice: The applicable legal framework for the present TSL implementation of the Trusted List of supervised/accredited Certification Service Providers for Slovenia is Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures and its implementation in Slovenia laws.

Veljavni pravni okvir za zadevno izvajanje TSL zanesljivega seznama nadzorovanih/akreditiranih overiteljev za Slovenijo je Direktiva Evropskega parlamenta in Sveta 1999/93/ES z dne 13. decembra 1999 o okviru Skupnosti za elektronski podpis in njeno izvajanje v zakonodaji Slovenije.
